## Content Rules
1. All user-facing text MUST be in Hebrew
2. Keep brand name "Purcari" in English
3. Use ₪ symbol for prices: `₪{price}`
4. Format: `₪180` (no space between symbol and number)
5. Product names have dual fields: use `productNameHe` for display
